text: Géraldine Mahieu (born 15 September 1993) is a French water polo player. She was a member of the France women's national water polo team at the 2015 World Aquatics Championships and 2017 World Aquatics Championships. == References == == Other website == * geraldine-mahieu-est-entree Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:French water polo players Category:People from Nord Category:Sportspeople from Hauts-de-France
